Add secret key in Configuration service
E.g  encrypt.key=secreteKeyThatShouldBeKeptSafeInADifferentPlace

Encrypt
http://localhost:8888/encrypt
Write text to encrypt in body of the request.
Take the encrypted string and put it in configs file
E.g   msg: "{cipher}66d8e0c52c7816b61e97b3dae7a029c1b8b946e42af4f1d3a03c361f4eb7ae79"

Decrypt
http://localhost:8888/decrypt
Put the encrypted string in the body of the request